{"tid":2335501,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐洲密封 550 萬年洞穴　發現全新無色素有毒蜈蚣　命名為「洞穴之王」","createTime":"2020-12-22T02:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T09:23:47.000Z","uid":141151,"like":107,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"d501fb69fd1c151b1824484d4c1fc72f33b3f9f7","tid":2335501,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T02:53:51.000Z","msg":"歐洲密封 550 萬年洞穴　發現全新無色素有毒蜈蚣　命名為「洞穴之王」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/251561_web_jyU1b_1200x0.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F251561_web_jyU1b_1200x0.jpg&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FftobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=2fe99a64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F251561_web_jyU1b_1200x0.jpg&h=2a24eb28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/251561_web_jyU1b_1200x0.jpg</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zVtVpyS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzVtVpyS.jpg&h=022e9c75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/oo_487318_QwCas_1200x0.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Foo_487318_QwCas_1200x0.jpg&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FftobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=35b247b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Foo_487318_QwCas_1200x0.jpg&h=e80f10f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/oo_487318_QwCas_1200x0.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWQHO0D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWQHO0D.jpg&h=214ef04d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n羅馬尼亞東南部的 Movile 洞，相信不會是尋常人想去渡假的 wish list ，該洞無光線透入、空氣中充滿有毒的硫化氫、二氧化碳，以及低濃度的氧氣，在 1986 年被意外發現之前，已與外界隔絕約 550 萬年。不過，該地下生態系統中仍充滿生命。最新刊於 ZooKeys 的研究更指，發現 Movile 洞迄今已知的最大動物，命名為 Cryptops speleorex 的有毒蜈蚣長達 52 毫米，名字的意思則為「洞穴之王」。<br />\n<br />\n全文請前往立場<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/cosmos/%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%AF%86%E5%B0%81-550-%E8%90%AC%E5%B9%B4%E6%B4%9E%E7%A9%B4%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E5%85%A8%E6%96%B0%E7%84%A1%E8%89%B2%E8%9C%88%E8%9A%A3-%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D%E7%82%BA-%E6%B4%9E%E7%A9%B4%E4%B9%8B%E7%8E%8B/?fbclid=IwAR09RtZfUfE5GpLFNHiLuSOT73vIlBINvF_exJBi4fm-jyKUnRwN-gvjJI4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcosmos%2F%25E6%25AD%2590%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E5%25AF%2586%25E5%25B0%2581-550-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%25B4%259E%25E7%25A9%25B4%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%2589%25B2%25E8%259C%2588%25E8%259A%25A3-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%25BD%25E5%2590%258D%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E6%25B4%259E%25E7%25A9%25B4%25E4%25B9%258B%25E7%258E%258B%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR09RtZfUfE5GpLFNHiLuSOT73vIlBINvF_exJBi4fm-jyKUnRwN-gvjJI4&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FftobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=bf69c4a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcosmos%2F%25E6%25AD%2590%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E5%25AF%2586%25E5%25B0%2581-550-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%25B4%259E%25E7%25A9%25B4%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%2589%25B2%25E8%259C%2588%25E8%259A%25A3-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%25BD%25E5%2590%258D%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E6%25B4%259E%25E7%25A9%25B4%25E4%25B9%258B%25E7%258E%258B%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR09RtZfUfE5GpLFNHiLuSOT73vIlBINvF_exJBi4fm-jyKUnRwN-gvjJI4&h=c5b74325\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/cosmos/%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%AF%86%E5%B0%81-550-%E8%90%AC%E5%B9%B4%E6%B4%9E%E7%A9%B4%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E5%85%A8%E6%96%B0%E7%84%A1%E8%89%B2%E8%9C%88%E8%9A%A3-%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D%E7%82%BA-%E6%B4%9E%E7%A9%B4%E4%B9%8B%E7%8E%8B/?fbclid=IwAR09RtZfUfE5GpLFNHiLuSOT73vIlBINvF_exJBi4fm-jyKUnRwN-gvjJI4</a>"},{"pid"